clash_faq_schedule_1_header: WHEN EXACTLY DO I NEED TO BE THERE?
clash_faq_schedule_1_paragraph: Each day, [{{minutes}}] minutes before matches start, all team members must verify they are ready to participate by "Locking In" for the day's events. This ensures only teams with full rosters are included in the Bracket.
clash_faq_schedule_2_header: WHAT DO I DO IF I DON'T WIN BUT WANT TO KEEP PLAYING?
clash_faq_schedule_2_paragraph: Each day of Clash is a new event and can be played by anyone, even if your team lost or didn't participate in the previous day. Teams who won the previous day's Bracket will face off against each other, so you are free to tweak your approach for a new set of opponents.
clash_faq_prizing_caption_1: Your Team's Skill Tier increases the level of prizing in Clash loot.
clash_faq_prizing_caption_2: Wins within a bracket improve the contents inside Clash loot.
clash_faq_prizing_caption_3: Bracket wins improve the tier of all your Clash loot.
clash_faq_prizing_caption_4: Tickets directly increase the number of Clash Caches you will earn.
clash_faq_prizing_caption_5: Every bracket win grants an increasingly cool in-game trophy available for two weeks.
clash_faq_prizing_1_header: HOW DO I EARN THE GOOD PRIZES?
clash_faq_prizing_1_paragraph: Your Clash Cache will become more powerful with each win, increasing the rarity of its contents. When your Team wins a Bracket, the cache is upgraded and the contents increase more than ever. Keep feeding your cache with wins to maximize your prizing output.
clash_faq_prizing_2_header: ARE MY PRIZES GETTING BETTER AS I PROGRESS THROUGH THE BRACKET?
clash_faq_prizing_2_paragraph: When you win a Bracket, the contents of your Clash Cache get an incredible upgrade and carry through to the next day. Losing a Bracket means you can open your cache now, but without the significant upgrade Bracket winners enjoy.
clash_faq_prizing_3_header: WHEN DO I GET MY STUFF ALREADY?
clash_faq_prizing_3_paragraph_a: When you complete a day of Clash games you will be able to open any unlocked Clash Caches and VP prizes you have earned. When your Team goes undefeated and wins the whole Bracket, your Clash Cache is upgraded and can be unlocked another day.
clash_faq_prizing_3_paragraph_b: Should you go undefeated all three days, your supremely upgraded Clash Cache will unlock when it senses it has reached full capacity.
clash_faq_requirements_1_header: WHY DO I NEED AN ENTRY TICKET TO JOIN?
clash_faq_requirements_1_paragraph: Clash is the most competitive mode to date and includes the most competitive rewards model ever. Like with many tournament formats, your entry is added to the prize pool and distributed throughout. By picking up a few wins, your Clash Cache already contains far more than the value of a single Ticket.
clash_faq_requirements_2_header: DO I NEED TO BE LEVEL 30/HONORABLE/ETC?
clash_faq_requirements_2_paragraph: All players must be at least level 30, have played all placement matches in one Ranked Queue, and be at least Honor 2 to participate in Clash.
clash_faq_requirements_3_header: DO I NEED TO PLAY RANKED?
clash_faq_requirements_3_paragraph: Clash requires that all participants have at least dipped their toe in the competititve environment by getting placed in any Ranked Queue. Your rating in Ranked will help determine your initial placement in the Tournmaent Skill Tiers as well.
clash_faq_requirements_4_header: HOW CAN I AVOID PAYING FOR THE TICKET/IS CLASH NOT FREE?
clash_faq_requirements_4_paragraph: Tickets can be acquired for free by participating in Ranked Flex games while you have the Clash Mission or by spending Blue Essence instead of RP in the store. Purchasing with RP is the only other way to acquire new tickets, but you can always receive a ticket from a friend during Clash Registration.
clash_faq_progression_caption_hint_vp: Each Clash win earns you VP at the end of the day. Once you have the required VP you will unlock the next reward.
clash_faq_progression_1_header: HOW DO I GET MORE VICTORY POINTS?
clash_faq_progression_1_paragraph: VP is earned exclusively for winning Clash games. Additional VP is awarded for your first win each week a Clash is held. The only way to get more games in a given week is to keep winning, only undefeated players will reach the final round on Sunday.
clash_faq_progression_2_header: DO I KEEP MY VICTORY POINTS AFTER A CLASH HAS ENDED?
clash_faq_progression_2_paragraph: Victory Points earn you rewards based on the current Faction sponsoring the Clash. Earn as many as you can in both weekends to progress as far as possible along the VP rewards track. When a new Faction steps in to sponsor a Clash, all VP is reset and you will start earning towards the new Faction's rewards.
clash_faq_skill_tiers_1_header: WHY DID I GET PLACED IN TIER X?
clash_faq_skill_tiers_1_paragraph: Because Clash allows players of a wider range of skill to form Teams, the way we match your Team against others varies slightly from Ranked as well. By first placing teams into a Skill Tier based on Team MMR, we can then focus on making great brackets as well as great matches.
clash_faq_skill_tiers_2_header: WHY DID MY TIER CHANGE BEFORE MY TEAM FINISHED REGISTERING?
clash_faq_skill_tiers_2_paragraph: As players are added to your Team, Clash reassesses your Skill Tier to ensure you are put into a competitive Bracket.
clash_faq_skill_tiers_3_header: CAN I INVITE ANY PERSON ONTO MY TEAM?
clash_faq_skill_tiers_3_paragraph: Though we encourage Players to fill their Team with five close friends, we know that is not possible for many players. Other members of your Team may make suggestions from their friends list as well, but as a last resort you are always free to send an invite to a new acquaintance not on your list.
clash_faq_re_entry_1_paragraph: Teams that fail to secure a Trophy on a given day unlock and may open their Clash Caches.
clash_faq_advancement_1_header: WHY DIDN'T I ADVANCE TO THE 8-TEAM BRACKET?
clash_faq_advancement_1_paragraph: Only those who claim the Trophy for their current bracket are upgraded for the following day. However, you may still return and battle a new set of foes each day to try and claim the Trophy and earn your way to the next Bracket.
clash_faq_advancement_2_header: DO I HAVE TO PLAY MORE GAMES IN THE LARGER BRACKETS?
clash_faq_advancement_2_paragraph: 4-Team Brackets always consist of 2 games. Once you reach the 8-Team Bracket you have the opportunity for up to 3 games and in 16-Team Brackets you can play at most 4 games. However, any time a team reaches two losses their day is over regardless of the number of wins.
